encounters.summary:
{
  "narration": "In a fierce skirmish near the Hidden Entrance to the Dwarven Complex, your party bravely faced three snarling giant rats that burst from the shadows. Gilly struck first, slashing a rat with her shortsword, followed by Elara's precise arrow taking down the same beast. Thalor joined with a solid warhammer blow, but was bitten in retaliation. You, Norn, delivered the finishing blow with a powerful strike of your longsword, felling the last rat despite a counterattack that wounded Elara. With the rats defeated and the tunnel momentarily safe, your companions catch their breath and ready for what lies ahead. Each member of your party—including yourself, Gilly, Elara, and Thalor—has gained 18 experience points for this victory, a total of 75 XP split among you all. The slain giant rats leave behind only silence and the echoes of battle as you prepare to proceed.",
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "R14-E1",
        "changes": "All three giant rats have been defeated, their statuses set to 'dead' with hit points at or below zero."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "updateNPCInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "npcName": "Elara",
        "changes": "Elara loses 5 hit points from the giant rat's bite."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "exit",
      "parameters": {}
    }
  ]
}

{
  "narration": "In the tense skirmish near the Hidden Entrance to the Dwarven Complex, your party bravely faced two hostile goblins emerging from the shadows. After the first goblin wounded you with a well-placed arrow causing 6 points of piercing damage, Gilly swiftly retaliated with a deadly shortsword strike enhanced by her sneak attack, cutting down the first goblin. The second goblin charged forward, only to be wounded by Elara's precise archery and then finished off by Thalor's powerful warhammer blow. With both goblins defeated and their bodies lying motionless in the cramped entrance, your party now has a moment to catch its breath and study the ancient dwarven door without immediate threat. Each member of your party, including you, Gilly, Elara, and Thalor, gains 25 experience points for this victory, totaling 100 XP. The path beyond the entrance awaits your next move.",
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updatePlayerInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "changes": "Norn loses 6 hit points from goblin's shortbow attack, current hit points now 30 out of 36. Norn gains 25 experience points."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "R14-E1",
        "changes": "First goblin loses 18 hit points from Gilly's shortsword attack including Sneak Attack, reduced to 0 HP and status changed to 'dead'. Second goblin loses 17 hit points from Elara's arrow and Thalor's warhammer attack, reduced to 0 HP and status changed to 'dead'. Both goblins are dead."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "updateNPCInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "npcName": "Gilly",
        "changes": "Gilly gains 25 experience points."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "updateNPCInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "npcName": "Elara",
        "changes": "Elara gains 25 experience points."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "updateNPCInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "npcName": "Thalor",
        "changes": "Thalor gains 25 experience points."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "exit",
      "parameters": {}
    }
  ]
}

